**Overview**  

This dashboard contains a unified metric and trend view of successful vs. failed logins for real-time authentication monitoring, session OS usage for platform-specific insights, top users to identify heavy usage and anomalies, a user activity map, and a top source IP table for geographic and security context.

[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/pulse_connect_secure/overview)
